metadata.description: I got shot by cupid, all it did was hurt! Prod by yours truly, featuring Kiddo. Enjoy! <3

lyrics.text:
I got shot by cupid
All it did was hurt
I think love is stupid
Only getting worse
Maybe it's a curse
Cuz it never works
I got shot by cupid
All it did was hurt

Quality, thats just what I need
You and me, I saw it in my dreams but you don't wanna be like that
You just lead me on like that

I'm calling but I see you don't have time though
You said its cuz you're in a different time zone
When you said I love you, must have been a typo
Cuz you haven't said it since and thats not right, no no no

I got shot by cupid
All it did was hurt
I think love is stupid
Only getting worse
Maybe it's a curse
Cuz it never works
I got shot by cupid
All it did was hurt

Sanity, I lose sanity
I could up and leave, but you're the remedy oh 
Arrows in behind my back
But you were still the best I had 
Yeah I know love ain't flawless
But I stay broken hearted 
You're pulling me apart when I should be in bed with you 
Want you all over me 
Wish you could set me free 
But you're still what I need, what I need

I got shot by cupid
All it did was hurt
I think love is stupid
Only getting worse
Maybe it's a curse
Cuz it never works
I got shot by cupid
All it did was hurt
